    program in the Research Scholar, Professor, or Short-Term Scholar categories.
    This includes scholars transferring-in from another institution. To request
    paperwork for a J-1 Student Intern program, see the J-1 Student Intern Request
    Form below. Administrator Applicant     DS-2019 Extension Form  To request paperwork to extend the stay of a J-1 Exchange
    Visitor in the Research Scholar or Professor categories. Administrator Applicant     No Patient Care Statement To be completed on department letterhead for any Exchange Visitors that possess foreign MDs.  Administrator    J-1 Student Intern Request Form  To request paperwork for a new J-1 Exchange Visitor in
    the Student Intern category, or to extend an existing Student Intern program. Administrator Applicant     J-1 Student Intern Evaluation Sample template for the required J-1 Student Intern program evaluation.  Administrator    J-1 Travel Signature Request Form  For J-1 Exchange Visitors already in the U.S. who need a
    travel signature for international travel or "out of country"
    authorization for a prolonged absence.  Applicant      J-1 Request to Add Dependent(s) Form    For J-1 Exchange Visitors already in the U.S. who would
    like to add a J-2 dependent spouse and/or children Applicant       J-1 Change of Funding Request Form  For J-1 Exchange Visitors already in the U.S. who need to
    report a change in funding. Applicant     J-1 Replace Lost DS-2019 Request Form For J-1 Exchange Visitors already in the U.S. who need to request a replacement of a lost, stolen or damaged DS-2019 form.  Applicant     J-1 Transfer Out Form For J-1 Exchange Visitors to request a transfer of their
    Exchange Visitor program from UIC to another U.S. institution. Administrator and Applicant    J-1 UIC Internal Transfer Form For J-1 Exchange Visitors to request an internal transfer from one UIC department to another.  Administrator and Applicant     J-1 Transfer In Request Form For J-1 Exchange Visitors intending to transfer to UIC from another institution or program. The Transfer In Form is included within our standard DS-2019 Request Form on page 4.     xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-16"? Skip Nav UICOIS Navigation Menu Home About OIS Students Faculty, Staff, and Scholars Travel & Visas J (Exchange Visitor) Information H (Specialty Occupation Worker) O-1 (Individuals of Extraordinary Ability) TN (Professionals Under NAFTA) E-3 (Australian Specialty Occupation Workers) Other Visa Statuses at UIC Pending LPR Forms Fulbright Foreign Student and Scholars (Non-U.S. Citizens) Visitors Departments Programs Life in Illinois Alumni Resources News   Office of International Services 1200 West Harrison Street Chicago, IL 60607-7161 Phone: (312) 996-3121 Email: ois@uic.edu Facebook Instagram Twitter Copyright ©  2018 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois | Web Privacy Statement Cookie Settings    